{"tid":980980,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有冇人想學古箏？","createTime":"2019-01-14T01:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T08:48:59.000Z","uid":16613,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"14f5f7fe378c09fa53b78fa1c19ccd7d781edfcd","tid":980980,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:42:05.000Z","msg":"十二年前開始學 當初雖然係畀人逼去學 不過慢慢發現古箏啲聲好好聽 而且我都鍾意同人夾歌 所以就繼續玩落去 有出過去校際音樂節玩吓比賽 我唔係啲咩大人物 所以但求拎表演經驗就好 中間亦都有出過去玩中樂團 當年係玩柏斯嘅中樂團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （而家已經冇咗，可能唔夠人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n由於上到大學少練咗好多 比起以前生疏好多 而家出咗黎做野又有其他野做 搞到冇乜時間去練返起去彈啲比較難嘅歌 同埋其實我唔太鍾意彈啲考級歌 我比較鍾意彈流行曲 但係因為古箏其實得5個音 所以要彈流行曲係幾大難度<br />\n<br />\n雖然生疏咗，不過教初學嘅話我都仲應付到嘅 如果你地有興趣想學嘅話就tg傾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Project_GZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FProject_GZ&d=bSFqEsVV1KvOTMWKz21YWNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5684c95e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Project_GZ</a>"},{"pid":"7cdebac7bc36746b154151eee08c3b13fca98d5c","tid":980980,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efd162494398510ae5788ebaf65f10a43979a9d","tid":980980,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61a2de92f5de53971d80948fa820f6adf04d47d","tid":980980,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177e1ff86f52322190d4d7afedfa3d66e8df11a5","tid":980980,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T02:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.g